# DEPRECATED — the operator's canonical .env now lives at the repo
# root (podman-compose's native location).  Use ./.env.example instead.
#
# Migration:
#   1. If you have a `deploy/.env` from a previous install,
#      `./acc-deploy.sh up` will auto-symlink it for one release; or
#      `mv deploy/.env .env` to do it explicitly.
#   2. For new installs:
#      cp .env.example .env
#      $EDITOR .env
#      ./acc-deploy.sh up
#
# This file is kept for one release as a pointer and will be removed.
